feat(api): :sparkles: add rate limiting

Why:
The API has no protection against abuse. A single client can
make unlimited requests, potentially causing service degradation
for all users and exhausting backend resources.

What:
Implement sliding window rate limiter middleware backed by Redis.
Default config allows 100 requests per 15-minute window per IP.
Returns 429 with Retry-After header when limit is exceeded.
Add middleware registration in app.ts and unit tests.

Ticket: PROJ-312
Signed-off-by: Alice Developer <alice@example.com>
